HEADWORD: canasta
<hw>canasta</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a form of rummy using two decks and
four jokers; jokers and deuces are wild; the object is to meld groups of
seven of the same rank.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> basket rummy, meld.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Canaster</ent>⟦br⟧
